### Health check (all UP)
GET http://localhost:7331/health

### Simulate cache failure
POST http://localhost:7331/demo/cache/down

### Health check (cache DOWN → 503)
GET http://localhost:7331/health

### Restore cache
POST http://localhost:7331/demo/cache/up

### Simulate database failure
POST http://localhost:7331/demo/database/down

### Health check (database DOWN → 503)
GET http://localhost:7331/health

### Restore database
POST http://localhost:7331/demo/database/up
